# Music Player

A simple music player application built with Python, pygame, and Tkinter.

![Music Player Screenshot](images/music-player.png)

## Features

- Browse and play music files in a specified directory
- Play/pause, stop, and skip to the next or previous track
- Shuffle mode to randomly play tracks
- Volume control using a slider
- Display of current track information

## Requirements

- Python 3.x
- pygame library
- Tkinter library

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

   ```shell
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/music-player.git
